de.mdelab.comparch

Interface MonitoredProperty

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchitecturalElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MonitoredPropertyImpl

    public interface MonitoredProperty
extends ArchitecturalElement
    A representation of the model object 'Monitored Property'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Architectural Element
    • Name
    • Type
    • Unit
    • Description
    • Value
    • Related Architectural Elements
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getMonitoredProperty()
